Class EOSCGCorrelationBackend

java.lang.Object
neqsim.thermo.util.gerg.EOSCGCorrelationBackend
public class EOSCGCorrelationBackend extends Object
EOS-CG correlation wrapper implemented using the EOSCGModel (based on GERG-2008 functional form).
